00:38:26,810 --> 00:38:27,770
The blade

588
00:38:27,770 --> 00:38:29,090
is still in your hand.

589
00:38:42,050 --> 00:38:43,500
Guys,

590
00:38:43,500 --> 00:38:44,500
don’t you know

591
00:38:44,500 --> 00:38:45,830
what we are here for?

592
00:38:50,130 --> 00:38:52,270
That is to capture Yu Wenzhi alive.

593
00:38:53,290 --> 00:38:55,290
Ignore what’s happening in the Fortress.

594
00:38:55,290 --> 00:38:56,460
Think about it.

595
00:38:56,460 --> 00:38:58,020
Our members

596
00:38:58,020 --> 00:38:59,180
and Elders are all there.

597
00:38:59,180 --> 00:39:01,110
Aren’t they stronger than us?

598
00:39:01,940 --> 00:39:03,610
Hasn’t Shen Tianshu come before

599
00:39:04,700 --> 00:39:06,670
and got kicked out?

600
00:39:07,570 --> 00:39:09,090
That’s right.

601
00:39:09,460 --> 00:39:11,610
Divide yourselves into three groups.

602
00:39:11,610 --> 00:39:14,370
Take the civilians to safe places

603
00:39:14,370 --> 00:39:15,940
and protect them

604
00:39:15,940 --> 00:39:18,610
until we repulse Yu Wenzhi
and Demons’ attacks.

605
00:39:18,610 --> 00:39:19,530
-Yes.
-Yes.

606
00:39:21,020 --> 00:39:22,180
Follow me.

607
00:39:22,180 --> 00:39:23,610
This way. Let’s go.

608
00:39:24,740 --> 00:39:25,810
This way.

609
00:39:27,660 --> 00:39:29,940
How’s the Fortress?

610
00:39:44,850 --> 00:39:45,610
Sweetie,

611
00:39:45,610 --> 00:39:46,770
where are you going?

612
00:39:46,770 --> 00:39:48,220
I can join my elder brother

613
00:39:48,220 --> 00:39:50,290
to kill bad people and protect everyone.

614
00:39:51,810 --> 00:39:53,290
You’re brave.

615
00:39:53,700 --> 00:39:55,980
Can you promise me something?

616
00:39:56,420 --> 00:39:57,570
Yes.

617
00:39:57,570 --> 00:39:58,570
Come.

618
00:40:01,980 --> 00:40:03,130
Sit.

619
00:40:03,130 --> 00:40:04,420
Can you wait here?

620
00:40:04,420 --> 00:40:05,810
Your brother will pick you up

621
00:40:05,810 --> 00:40:07,500
once he wins the battle.

622
00:40:07,500 --> 00:40:08,420
Alright.

623
00:40:08,420 --> 00:40:09,220
From now on,

624
00:40:09,220 --> 00:40:10,770
you should practice hard

625
00:40:10,770 --> 00:40:13,260
to be a hero like him.

626
00:40:14,330 --> 00:40:16,260
Why haven’t we heard anything?

627
00:40:16,260 --> 00:40:18,020
How are they?

628
00:40:18,500 --> 00:40:19,770
Have they

629
00:40:19,770 --> 00:40:21,810
all been killed?

630
00:40:22,460 --> 00:40:24,090
What should we do?

631
00:40:26,420 --> 00:40:27,900
We’re doomed this time,

632
00:40:27,900 --> 00:40:30,090
aren’t we?

633
00:40:30,090 --> 00:40:31,980
We won’t surrender no matter what.

634
00:40:31,980 --> 00:40:33,610
If those bastards break in,

635
00:40:33,610 --> 00:40:36,420
I’ll kill them at all costs!

636
00:40:36,420 --> 00:40:40,610
Yes. Kill them at all costs!

637
00:40:40,610 --> 00:40:42,810
-Please bless us.
-Kill them at all costs!

638
00:40:42,810 --> 00:40:44,130
Calm down, everyone.

639
00:40:44,370 --> 00:40:45,900
Attention, please.

640
00:40:45,900 --> 00:40:47,370
Settle down.

641
00:40:47,370 --> 00:40:48,940
Look,

642
00:40:48,940 --> 00:40:51,420
others are outside
putting their lives on the line.

643
00:40:51,420 --> 00:40:53,660
How could we go out

644
00:40:53,660 --> 00:40:56,740
and distract them?

645
00:40:56,740 --> 00:40:58,610
We’d only be a burden.

646
00:40:58,610 --> 00:41:01,740
-That’s right.
-She’s right.

647
00:41:06,740 --> 00:41:08,610
Merciful Buddha.

648
00:41:18,330 --> 00:41:19,570
Fei,

649
00:41:19,570 --> 00:41:21,610
are you giving Yu Wenzhi up?

650
00:41:26,810 --> 00:41:27,850
I see.

651
00:41:28,330 --> 00:41:30,900
You’ve driven the others away.

652
00:41:30,900 --> 00:41:32,810
If there are moles among them,

653
00:41:32,810 --> 00:41:34,220
they’ll send wrong messages

654
00:41:34,220 --> 00:41:35,330
to buy us more time.

655
00:41:37,020 --> 00:41:39,180
We still have to try our best

656
00:41:39,180 --> 00:41:40,560
to seize Yu Wenzhi.

657
00:41:42,180 --> 00:41:43,290
Are there other ways

658
00:41:43,290 --> 00:41:44,610
to find him?

659
00:41:46,770 --> 00:41:48,710
Given the chaos we’ve caused,

660
00:41:49,980 --> 00:41:52,220
if my guess is correct,

661
00:41:52,940 --> 00:41:53,980
he’ll

662
00:41:53,980 --> 00:41:55,340
tighten the security.

663
00:41:56,330 --> 00:41:57,080
So

664
00:41:57,850 --> 00:41:59,700
he should be somewhere

665
00:41:59,700 --> 00:42:01,630
heavily guarded.

666
00:42:07,900 --> 00:42:08,850
Commander,

667
00:42:09,660 --> 00:42:10,850
they’ve got

668
00:42:10,850 --> 00:42:12,910
the civilians out.

669
00:42:15,810 --> 00:42:18,140
How come they didn’t rise to the bait?

670
00:42:18,660 --> 00:42:19,900
I think

671
00:42:19,900 --> 00:42:21,920
that’s only part of their plan.

672
00:42:30,500 --> 00:42:32,330
I guess

673
00:42:32,610 --> 00:42:34,050
they must’ve known

674
00:42:34,050 --> 00:42:36,130
that I’m somewhere else.

675
00:42:38,610 --> 00:42:40,740
Get Tianxian back.

676
00:42:40,740 --> 00:42:41,570
And

677
00:42:41,570 --> 00:42:44,120
tighten the security here

678
00:42:45,130 --> 00:42:47,460
for my safety.

679
00:42:47,460 --> 00:42:49,090
I’ll arrange the best members

680
00:42:49,090 --> 00:42:50,250
of Mingfeng to protect you.

681
00:43:01,420 --> 00:43:02,270
Go south.

682
00:43:04,850 --> 00:43:05,770
Hey,

683
00:43:05,770 --> 00:43:06,760
