684
00:43:08,420 --> 00:43:09,940
Just tell me left or right, can’t you?

685
00:43:20,330 --> 00:43:21,290
While we patrol,

686
00:43:21,290 --> 00:43:22,460
you take care of master,

687
00:43:22,460 --> 00:43:22,980
understand?

688
00:43:22,980 --> 00:43:23,770
<i>Stationery</i>
Yes.

689
00:43:23,770 --> 00:43:24,700
Let’s go.

690
00:43:42,660 --> 00:43:43,850
Our men

691
00:43:43,850 --> 00:43:45,980
