692
00:43:45,980 --> 00:43:47,380
No one can get in.

693
00:43:48,570 --> 00:43:49,480
Good.

694
00:43:55,420 --> 00:43:57,280
Anything about
the Fortress of the Forty-Eight?

695
00:43:59,740 --> 00:44:00,840
Not yet.

696
00:44:01,610 --> 00:44:03,700
According to the spy sent previously,

697
00:44:03,700 --> 00:44:05,180
the South Blade’s granddaughter Zhou Fei

698
00:44:05,180 --> 00:44:08,220
