699
00:44:08,980 --> 00:44:09,740
And she’s

700
00:44:09,740 --> 00:44:11,020
with a young man

701
00:44:11,020 --> 00:44:13,220
whose footwork is excellent.

702
00:44:17,020 --> 00:44:20,150
A young man with excellent footwork.

703
00:44:21,740 --> 00:44:22,550
What’s wrong?

704
00:44:24,740 --> 00:44:26,020
Nothing.

705
00:44:26,020 --> 00:44:26,850
That reminds me

706
00:44:26,850 --> 00:44:28,670
